Cura Foresight is a full-stack web application built using the MERN stack with blockchain integration.

Frontend:
- React
- Tailwind CSS
- Vite

Backend:
- Node.js
- Express.js

Database:
- MongoDB

Blockchain:
- Hardhat (Smart Contracts)

 Features
- Responsive frontend built with React
- RESTful APIs using Express
- MongoDB database integration
- Smart contract deployment and interaction
- Modular backend structure (controllers, models, routes)


